{"tid":741903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士輾石屎彈穿車底傷客","createTime":"2018-07-14T06:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T06:22:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"147b24b1ddc05797f54821402f867cdb520afef6","tid":741903,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180714/20449530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F20449530&d=MBCC1P8dhh1GJTx746BO8jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6e1df048\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180714%2F20449530&h=cffc9bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180714/20449530</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月14日 <br />\n<br />\n巴士輾石屎彈穿車底傷客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180714/large/14la4p08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180714%2Flarge%2F14la4p08.jpg&h=baf54052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■巴士車底石屎柱撞穿，關愛座遭撞歪。溫瑞麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中環發生罕見巴士意外！一輛九巴昨晚沿德輔道中行駛途中，疑輾過一段損毀路面，其間一塊鬆脫的巨型石屎被輾起撞穿車底，直插入車廂下層樓梯後面一排關愛座座位的台階，導致該排關愛座翻倒壓向後一排座位的乘客。一名女乘客受傷需送院，警員正調查事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乘客拉開座位救人<br />\n<br />\n涉事九巴為978號線，由灣仔北駛往粉嶺華明總站。事發於昨晚約9時，當時巴士沿德輔道中慢線行駛至26號對開，正開往下一站利源東街準備埋站落客。<br />\n<br />\n未料巴士右邊車輪疑輾過介乎慢線與中線之間的一段損毀路面，一塊約一米長乘半米闊的鬆脫石屎疑被輾至彈起，撞穿巴士右邊車底，繼而直插入下層車廂內，車長知道事發即時停車。<br />\n<br />\n意外中，巴士下層車廂樓梯後面關愛座座位的台階，被石屎撞至翻倒，並壓向後面一對座位。現場消息指，當時座位坐着一名女乘客，被翻倒的關愛座夾着，一度撫着右邊腰部，受傷叫痛。其他熱心乘客見狀遂合力拉開座位救人。<br />\n<br />\n從現場所見，被輾起石屎的地面遺下一個大窿，路面亦出現多條裂痕。幸受傷女乘客傷勢不嚴重，事後由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫瑞麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n認紅磡站未拆除螺絲膠蓋<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n插針狂徒殺入港島新巴線"},{"pid":"7cc53094fe4248ce031ff9ffdc6b6b0266b7c80e","tid":741903,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4376e69fe38362356aaaf418948f61398208e7","tid":741903,"uid":78873,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"土地公公擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9302df2236b03959d4b866551d35d0b8450bce85","tid":741903,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"整定"},{"pid":"f568a14e2cc7dd0ed6180ef119aa6b786a6a0ccf","tid":741903,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>導致該排關愛座翻倒壓向後一排座位的乘客。一名女乘客受傷需送院，警員正調查事件原因。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b65437b288bccbefff4c7a8cb551c3d9366e941","tid":741903,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"以後講 俾你坐先反正你坐得唔係幾耐<br />\n已經有例證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6136ca060b122f09f7d91036a07724979978b9a","tid":741903,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"只需要兩蚊就可以送老友記上天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6954ba5fbc4401d69239a63cf4ff09c7138aff35","tid":741903,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"追擊關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a447258bbe8abdba6ea111c578ad5d72cabbd436","tid":741903,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6954ba5fbc4401d69239a63cf4ff09c7138aff35","tid":741903,"u